14 from said such lands, plus cash bonus, of the royalty in said such
15 leases. Such The Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall
16 give notice of its intention to offer for sale said such lease or
17 drilling contract by advertising said such fact for a period of at
18 least twenty-one (21) days electronically on an authorized state
19 website and in a legal newspaper published and of general
20 circulation in the county where said such lands are located. The
21 Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall award such lease,
22 leases, or drilling contracts to the highest responsible bidder.
23 All bidding shall be by sealed written or electronic bids filed with
24 said the Office of Management and Enterprise Services.
