17 Planning Act and such agencies shall respond and provide any such
18 assistance as may be required. The Commission may use existing
19 studies, surveys, plans, data, and other materials in the possession
20 of any state agency. Each such agency shall make the same available
21 to the Commission so that the Commission may have available to it
22 current information with respect to the capital plans and programs
23 of each such agency.
